data.description:
Like-New Home Now Available in Charming Vintage Springs!! This 2017 built home features a great room with double tray ceiling that is open to the kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The split bedroom plan has three bedrooms with plush carpeting that your toes will appreciate on chilly mornings, and 2 full baths PLUS a guest bath with pedestal sink. In addition to the bedrooms and living spaces there is also a Formal Dining Room AND an office!! This home has granite counters in both full baths and a huge master closet that you'll love. The master bath offers a dual granite vanity and separate tub and shower. Outside, you will find a fully fenced backyard and a patio area that is partially covered. Vintage Springs is a gated community in a

Supreme Location within 5 minutes of Midtown, Downtown, Central Hattiesburg & Quick Access to 1-59, Hwy 98 & Hwy 49! MANY school options as well - PCS and Sacred Heart private schools & in the Dixie School System. Vintage Springs is an established community with street lights, park settings, sidewalks & more, allowing you to live a comfortable life in an efficient home!! Schedule your viewing today!
